---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---
<MainLayout>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-10">
    <p class="text-lg text-black my-1 tracking-[0.02em] text-center mb-10">
      <span class="italic">about:</span> EMIL DOS SANTOS, BERTRAM BLAUENFELDT OTKJÆR OG VINCENT GROOS.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-10">
      <p class="text-lg text-black my-1 leading-relaxed text-left">
        Balash was born from a spontaneous idea shared by three friends—Bertram, Emil, and Vincent—whose paths first crossed in the world of hospitality.
        Emil, a chef driven by culinary creativity, crafts the flavors behind each experience. Bertram, a connoisseur of wine and impeccable service, ensures that every detail is seamlessly executed. Vincent, with expertise in event planning, brings their shared vision to life.
        What began as a single pop-up at Pio Vin has since evolved into a full-fledged event company, dedicated to curating gastronomic experiences that feel both intimate and unforgettable.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-black my-1 leading-relaxed text-left">
        What started as a single pop-up at Pio Vin has grown into a full-fledged event company, dedicated to crafting unforgettable gastronomic experiences.
        Rooted in the Arabic word for "giving without expectation," <span class="font-semibold">Balash</span> embodies our philosophy of generosity. While not free, our dining experiences feel like gifts—thoughtfully curated, rich in seasonal ingredients, and infused with warmth, quality, and a touch of Balash.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Sektioner med opdateret styling -->
    <div class="space-y-8 text-center">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg text-black my-1">( PRIVATE EVENTS )</h3>
        <hr class="border-t border-gray-300 mt-2" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg text-black my-1">( POP UP DINING )</h3>
        <hr class="border-t border-gray-300 mt-2" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg text-black my-1">( CATERING )</h3>
        <hr class="border-t border-gray-300 mt-2" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>


